#~ "Use of Jovie, the KDE text-to-speak program, to speak opponent’s moves"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Erabili Jovie, KDEren testu ahoskatze programa arerioaren mugimenduak "
#~ "ahoskatzeko"
